data.title: New York Yankees
data.meta_description: Vehicle license plate for fans of the New York Yankees.
data.text:
Online

You must have a valid New York State registration that does not expire within 60 days. This will have your current plate number and registration class code. See a sample registration document.

If your registration expires within the next 60 days, renew your registration online before you order.

Your name and address must be up to date with DMV. You can change your address online before you order.

You must have a credit or debit card that DMV accepts and a valid email address for confirmation purposes.

Order a New York Yankees Custom Plate Online

By Phone

You can order this plate by phone from the Custom Plates Unit at the phone number below.

By Mail

To order this plate by mail, use the Application for Custom Plates (PDF) (CP-30).

Mail the completed form and your payment to Custom Plates at the address below.

At a DMV Office
